---
/* ReferenceDesk (Site Update v7, Sub-agent C — Standard Mode footer surface).

   Small dignified "On the Reference Desk" block listing the two human
   librarians the public can write to. Mounted by the orchestrator on the
   homepage and the Reading Room landing.

   Library-institutional register (per repo memory): no case names, no
   court numbers, no /court/* links. Dave's role line says "OASTL
   litigation" because Reference Desk sits in the library-card register
   the encyclopedia keeps for institutional surfaces — close enough to be
   honest, far enough not to telegraph litigation. Margaret's role stays
   editorial.

   Hidden in Reference Mode by Sub-agent B's preempt rule on
   `.reference-desk`. Visible in Standard Mode and Library Mode.

   Component-scoped styles below; mode-standard.css duplicates the
   essentials so the component still renders well if loaded outside the
   layouts that pull mode-standard.css. The duplication is deliberate —
   peers can mount this component anywhere.
*/
---
<aside class="reference-desk" aria-label="On the Reference Desk">
  <div class="rd-eyebrow">On the Reference Desk</div>
  <ul class="rd-list">
    <li class="rd-person">
      <div class="rd-name">Margaret Bird</div>
      <div class="rd-role">Editorial calibration; school-trust scholarship</div>
      <a class="rd-cta" href="/contribute/">Get in touch with Margaret</a>
    </li>
    <li class="rd-person">
      <div class="rd-name">Dave Sullivan</div>
      <div class="rd-role">Library architecture; trust-records research</div>
      <a class="rd-cta" href="/contribute/">Get in touch with Dave</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</aside>

<style>
  .reference-desk {
    background: var(--linen-card, #FFFDF7);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule-border, #D8D1C2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
    max-width: 65ch;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--old-gold, #B88A2E);
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem 2rem;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-person {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-person .rd-name {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--deep-navy, #1F2A44);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-person .rd-role {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink, #17202A);
    opacity: 0.8;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-cta {
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--deep-navy, #1F2A44);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }
  .reference-desk .rd-cta:hover {
    color: var(--trust-blue, #1D4F7C);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .reference-desk .rd-list {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
